Her Sentence Was Hard Time, Her Revenge Came Easy!

When Kristy's (jessica drake) boyfriend dumps her, her silly obsession with winning him back lands her in jail. While on the inside, she makes unlikely friends with a crazy cast of ...    Full Descriptioncharacters. Her new friends teach her a new way of looking at life and when she gets out, she puts her knowledge to work. Empowered, Kristy starts an agency that offers women a chance at revenge, often with hilarious results but without the possibility of prison.
